00:02:45.240 --> 00:02:49.320
 This is scientifically the case.

00:02:49.320 --> 00:02:53.160
 - You mean just art as in painted or does the podcast count?

00:02:53.160 --> 00:02:54.880
 - Oh, is it art form?

00:02:54.880 --> 00:02:55.720
 - It's an art form.

00:02:55.720 --> 00:02:56.560
 - Is it?

00:02:56.560 --> 00:02:57.400
 - It is.

00:02:57.400 --> 00:02:59.520
 (laughing)

00:02:59.520 --> 00:03:02.960
 - In this particular case, it's art paintings,

00:03:02.960 --> 00:03:05.240
 as opposed to art podcasts.

00:03:05.240 --> 00:03:09.400
 This was a scientific paper that was released in November 2019

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:13.160
 and it was called Bullshit Makes the Art Grow Profounder.

00:03:13.160 --> 00:03:14.160
 And what they did was--

00:03:14.160 --> 00:03:15.000
 - Lost.

00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:15.840
 - Lost.

