 - Coming from me, that is a lot.

00:03:23.240 --> 00:03:27.040
 They did a study where they show different bits of art

00:03:27.040 --> 00:03:28.640
 and they gave them different names.

00:03:28.640 --> 00:03:31.240
 So one piece had a very mundane name,

00:03:31.240 --> 00:03:33.080
 but then the next person might see the same piece

00:03:33.080 --> 00:03:36.080
 and it had an interesting name that might make them go,

00:03:36.080 --> 00:03:39.360
 ooh, something like the Death Echo, right?

00:03:39.360 --> 00:03:40.720
 - I think this completely makes sense.

