 So they found it more meaningful, right?

00:03:42.200 --> 00:03:44.000
 - This is, I guess they were just testing this idea

00:03:44.000 --> 00:03:45.720
 that if you give something a pretentious name,

00:03:45.720 --> 00:03:46.720
 it doesn't add to it. - Another question.

