 - Hmm, very defensive.

00:04:08.640 --> 00:04:11.160
 - How do you determine pretentious?

00:04:11.160 --> 00:04:13.920
 Who's deciding whether Death Echo is pretentious?

00:04:13.920 --> 00:04:15.200
 - Good call, what is pretentious?

00:04:15.200 --> 00:04:16.400
 I think that's a really good question.

00:04:16.400 --> 00:04:18.160
 I found myself asking it at the whole time

00:04:18.160 --> 00:04:19.000
 as I was reading this.

00:04:19.000 --> 00:04:20.320
 - Did the study answer it?

00:04:20.320 --> 00:04:23.480
 - Oh, well, I think pretentious means

00:04:23.480 --> 00:04:27.520
 it's completely unrelated to the content of the work, right?

00:04:27.520 --> 00:04:29.560
 So if it's a painting of a lemon,

00:04:29.560 --> 00:04:31.500
 and I call it Sicilian Dreams,

00:04:31.500 --> 00:04:33.880
 you know, Sicily grows a lot of lemons, right?

00:04:33.880 --> 00:04:35.920
 That's a normal-ish title, I see.

00:04:35.920 --> 00:04:39.000
 Whereas if I call it a grandfather,

