 - It is the way he said it.

00:04:44.280 --> 00:04:46.400
 All right, the well, the well of sorrows,

00:04:46.400 --> 00:04:49.400
 then that is, it's much less related

00:04:49.400 --> 00:04:50.600
 to the content of the picture.

00:04:50.600 --> 00:04:52.280
 - But if you call it shit sandwich,

00:04:52.280 --> 00:04:54.280
 that's not pretentious even though it's not related.

00:04:54.280 --> 00:04:55.960
 - I think it can be, I think it can be pretentious.

00:04:55.960 --> 00:04:57.280
 - Yeah, okay, very much.

00:04:57.280 --> 00:04:59.960
 - It's a bit, this is all mentioned in my new podcast.

00:04:59.960 --> 00:05:01.440
 What is pretentious?

00:05:01.440 --> 00:05:03.800
 (buzzer)

